OL,3,CTaxi driver 'acting the hardman' jailed
OL,5,FA former Fonacab taxi driver who
OL,6,Fassaulted and threatened a front seat
OL,7,Fpassenger with an imitation firearm
OL,8,Fwhilst he was under the influence of
OL,9,Fcocaine was jailed for 10 months.
OL,11,FBrian Alexander Stalford - who
OL,12,Fadmitted he was 'acting the hardman' -
OL,13,Fwill spend an additional 10 months on
OL,14,Flicence when is released from custody.
OL,16,FThe 49-year old father-of-two, from
OL,17,FPark Avenue in east Belfast, pleaded
OL,18,Fguilty to a charge of possessing an
OL,19,Fimitation firearm with intent to cause
OL,20,Ffear of violence and was sentenced by
OL,21,FJudge Donna McColgan KC.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
