OL,3,CTaxi driver 'acting the hardman' jailed
OL,5,FDuring Tuesday's hearing, it emerged
OL,6,Fthat Stalford issued the threat to the
OL,7,Ffront-seat passenger over a drugs debt.
OL,9,FHis barrister Sean Devine said the
OL,10,F"supreme irony" of the incident was
OL,11,Fthat Stalford issued the threat to pay
OL,12,Foff his own drugs debt, and was under
OL,13,Fthe influence of cocaine at the time.
OL,15,FBelfast Crown Court heard that between
OL,16,FMarch and June 2023 Stalford worked as
OL,17,Fa taxi driver for Fonacab in Belfast.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
