OL,3,CTaxi driver 'acting the hardman' jailed
OL,5,FOn a date between March 1 and June 2,
OL,6,F2023, dashcam footage was recorded in
OL,7,Fhis vehicle of himself driving with
OL,8,Ftwo male passengers on board in
OL,9,FHolywood.
OL,11,FThe recording captured Stalford in
OL,12,Fpossession of an imitation handgun
OL,13,Fresembling a 'Desert Eagle' self-
OL,14,Floading pistol.
OL,16,FDuring the journey, whilst brandishing
OL,17,Fthe imitation firearm with intent to
OL,18,Fcause fear of violence, Stalford told
OL,19,Fthe front seat passenger 'you are
OL,20,Flucky I'm not taking your f*****g
OL,21,Fknees out as that's the mood I'm in'.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
