OL,3,CTaxi driver 'acting the hardman' jailed
OL,5,FStalford also told the male 'what
OL,6,Fhappens in the car stays in the car'
OL,7,Fand threatened to take his head off.
OL,9,FAfter making a reference to the male's
OL,10,Ffriend, who was in the back seat of
OL,11,Fthe taxi, Stalford then struck the
OL,12,Ffront-seat passenger in the face with
OL,13,Fthe imitation firearm.
OL,15,FFollowing this, Stalford told the
OL,16,Ffront-seat passenger to 'do what you
OL,17,Fdo and you make up what you f*****g
OL,18,Fneed to make up quickly. You work your
OL,19,Ff*****g debt off.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
