OL,3,CTaxi driver 'acting the hardman' jailed
OL,5,FThis, the court heard, was in relation
OL,6,Fto a drugs debt.
OL,8,FRevealing how the footage came to be
OL,9,Fin the public domain was not known,
OL,10,FJudge McColgan said Stalford was
OL,11,Farrested on June 1, 2023.
OL,13,FDuring an interview with police, he
OL,14,Fgave a 'no comment' response but did
OL,15,Fprovide a pre-prepared statement in
OL,16,Fwhich he denied being in possession of
OL,17,Fan imitation firearm and assaulting
OL,18,Fanyone.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
