OL,3,CTaxi driver 'acting the hardman' jailed
OL,5,FStalford said a friend had left the
OL,6,Fimitation firearm in his vehicle and
OL,7,Fthat on the day in question he was
OL,8,Funder the influence of cocaine and
OL,9,Fused the item in an attempt to
OL,10,Fintimidate the front-seat passenger to
OL,11,Fpay money he owed to a friend.
OL,13,FIn addition, Stalford told probation
OL,14,Fthe threatening behavior was 'out of
OL,15,Fcharacter' and that he was 'acting the
OL,16,Fhardman'.
OL,18,FNoting Stalford has 66 previous
OL,19,Fconvictions, Judge McColgan said this
OL,20,Fincluded two prior charges for
OL,21,Fpossessing an offensive weapon.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/10
